      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The prices of domestic liquefied petroleum (LP) gas cylinders will be further reduced next week, Chairman of Litro Gas Lanka Limited, Muditha Peiris says.",
        "According to Mr. Peiris, the price reduction is expected to come into effect on Monday (Sep 05)."
